### Naming Convention
$MOS_TARGET/[V_TARG]/mos_target_twomass_psc-[NUM].fits, where V_TARG=1.0.1 for DR18; and NUM = 1..1 to partition the file into parts

### Enviroments

### Approximate Size

### File Type

### Generated by Product
